com.upsight.android.analytics.provider

Class UpsightUserAttributes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.upsight.android.analytics.provider.UpsightUserAttributes

  • public abstract class UpsightUserAttributes
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract class providing a static methods to set User Attributes. Requires the user attributes to each be specified in the Android Manifest at compile time as meta-data in the format

    Supports values of types String, Integer, Boolean, and Float.
